description: Surveys of the marine habitats along the South-East,East and North-West coasts of Barbados from inter tidal zone to the 50 metre depth contour. Using walkover , scuba diving and snorkel survey techniques.The extents were from Maycocks Bay, between Harrison Point and Arawak Cement plant to South Point . This data was provided by in August 1998.
name: TM-BRB_Benthic Habitat (South and East Coast)-1998-1:5000
